{"tid":1501423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到速狗唔可以再退","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:22:24.000Z","uid":198258,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d14c9e1ddd9e1084cec8e01706daa183e654ea2","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"每一次見到速狗衝前，個個嚇到向後跑，總有一兩個唔夠快/跌親，比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n速狗跑得快係因為輕裝，姐係唔挨得打。<br />\n防暴高防，所以跑唔快。<br />\n<br />\n但係大家見到速狗就同佢鬥跑，見到防暴就set rb 對打。點解係都要同人地嘅強項對冚？<br />\n<br />\n我知已經有好多個post講過好多次，見到速狗應該係大嗌救人，唔係嗌走佬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">下次見到速狗要點做呀？</span>"},{"pid":"4270f7c474682ce9694c7088571a0aa40cbc5602","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"一定要改見速狗就走呢個反射動作，又唔係唔夠打。"},{"pid":"a7cb99db9b4307c578d8a15fc37dee286a65f052","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"1919de946a1a4fd667d3dd981a2594e0b174fe6e","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c442edf2ed9f9cfeb0af77ee75c54177e4ec057","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:05:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb675891ffba3405cd4a2a96d91a1b4816f20f66","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a2e64e905152f5a0f6376e94e31de2572dcd893","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c95651e244bf4d7b316e3c1dee52e48421ae195d","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e479422411bd86de15e4a24a72c77f657042dc29","tid":1501423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:06:16.000Z",